\id REV
\ide  UTF-8
\h Dukum Yuwana 
\toc1 Dukum Yuwana 
\toc2 Dukum Yuwana 
\toc3 rev 
\mt1 Dukum Yuwana  
\c 1
\p
\v 1 Wonco dukum yeecu almasiyabwuro kwaama neckri many bunebcebnin dikero abwiuti to kutangbeu. Cidang euro kin tomangeu ci twomuu nii tomangece fiye bwerang'a CE yuwana wife.  
\v 2 Yuwana ma warke kwaaa mares kange wark are dor yeecu Almasiya.  
\v 3 Uil be buyere nilwo kiye bifumerowoti kidireu kibi kwaneu, kange birowbo nuwa kerdukmerowoti bwangtem bwangten dike cil bulangi wore cetiyeu, wori kumenin dadom.  
\v 4 Mo yuwana, ki loniwabe kwoama niber buten Asiya! luma fiy'e kom wiye fuwor neret wuro naweu, wuor nowi nanduwo, co cabouti fokabe, qluwa tangbeko biro niber kabum tor kutile ceveu,  
\v 5 fo yeecu Almasi'yann, nil warke kinero yor yeveu, bwe kaba kwenta buwarek, nii ma liyar liyabera dorbitineve tiye. Niiwo cwiboti ceerbo bwirankevet be ki buyacece takeu.  
\v 6 Yilam yokenbo wob liyarebceb, nob kwa ama ceb kange teeceduktangka kange bikw amliyaret kino fiye awiye diri, afi nyo.  
\v 7 To, bouti wari kange bilorinim, nuwe kwarub antoco, kange nubo wuro kwevceu wuyak. gwamm mwan unbero dor bitineveeu ciiyanma bwatum kercer. Nyo, ati nyo.  
\v 8 “Mo kabako mo bwiko in nuwa kwaama Teluma, wuro inco cinaweu, inco cinowi namduweu, co cabouti fo kutangbo take, nii bikwan liyaret gwamm.”  
\v 9 Mo, yuoaua-kekume kange womwer kang kangtimor nuwa dotange, kange liyro kange birom nerembo mor yeecu-mi dor diiyelero coti batmuca wori ker kwaamar kange wake yeecu cee.  
\v 10 Mi mor yuwa tangbe ki kume teluwe. dila nuwa dik diro kange tribi kwan na cume fo bwini.  
\v 11 yiki, inudang dika mwa toweu mor bifumeve, natumg lowabe kwaamaro niber Afisu, wo simirns, wo Birgamas, wo Tayatira, wo sardisu, wo filadalfiya, kange wo laudiku'ya.”  
\v 12 min yila nan nuwa dirowo yiye kero tiyui, mi yilari laminto talkir niber dor diker timer cer.  
\v 13 Tiber talkirnin kangewi cerkang niffiv, dumki kulerdo cwemer wuro ya cumom naceke, bwamki kulewdo cwemer wuor ya cumom nace ke, bwamfidak wo mwindoceu kentang'um cantany ceko.  
\v 14 Jorcero kange yiri cero fuwoje fobfob na kulor-noa cwirir bititen kwaamar, nuweceu na biyen kirettak.  
\v 15 Namiceu na kwerum kwere na cii kwamkwabe kira kwabike, dircero na caji mwem wurmonkam.  
\v 16 Tanki brlivendo niber kange cattiyere min, kulendo carang caragau nyo yob cirouti nyico. Tikob cebo milbangti kam kambo kakauko kirnilbanre kambo keneu.  
\v 17 kikwama mitocem min yadti nacek na riiwo mankiyikii “nuware tan. mo kabako kange bwiko,  
\v 18 kange wo kidumeu. min buyam, dila to miki dume diri! miki nyilo buwarek kange fiye yoka dumekocetak.  
\v 19 Lanaworo mulang dike mutoweu, nikewo naweu, kange dike abwiuti bwiyoko wuro ninneu.  
\v 20 ki ker yurang'um yur ange wo bitirendoce riber muto kango cattiyere mirveu, kange frie trine talkir mwine nibereu! Bitirendo biro nibereu nobtomangeb lowabe kawawa niber, fu'te triner talkero niberewo inlowabe kwaama riber.   
\c 2
\p
\v 1 Na nii tomange lowabe kweama Aficu mulange birombo co kerobirom tamki bitiondo riber mor kangceko cattiyero rineu wo yamwi tiber diker timer takile mwine niber,  
\v 2 “Min nyemom dike mu maneu, kange datange mweu yobka nerer mweko kange nubo bwir min nyimom mun cuwanubowo yi dorciroti ki cin nob tomauges beu, dila kabo nye, mwa fiya cin nob cwerkeb.  
\v 3 Min nyimom mubiner nuwa dotange kambo kentak ker dner mir, dila luma nenbo  
\v 4 La dike mani nuwa luma mweko ti cikeu wo, mundubom cwika mweko kabak.  
\v 5 Lans wori, kwa fiy'e mu yarum wiyeu. Dubom nama dikertinimbo mu mani ki kabau. Dila dubom, manbo mwen na cokum talkire mwen fi'ye yimece.  
\v 6 La mun wiki wuro! ko dike nikolatawa matiyeu wuro miko keneu.  
\v 7 woki tuu nuwari a cwatuu dike yuwa tangbeksi lowabe kw aamatiyev cam turini di man dobco ci ca bitutti dumeu, firdauci kwaaws.””  
\v 8 Nawo bwetomange lowabe kwaams samirns mulaugi birombo co keti yawo cinco kabako co bwiko, wuro bwiyam no ki dume takeu.  
\v 9 Min nyiwom ditamge timin mwembo kange bwini' mweto dila munwi ki cweka min nyimon nubo kangetr birombo kin cin yafudawau, dila kebo nyo. ciin kuwabe bwekelkele.  
\v 10 Cware tai dotangero mweciten dorti fo kabeu: bwekelkeleu dodom a merken kange kumembo mor fucina, wori nacii cuwakom, kume keneu kan nuwa dotange nakumae kwobece. Komma dike dongdonge alam buwar man nekom lalang duwek dumek.  
\v 11 wuro ki tuuwer acwatuu dike yuwa tang ko yi lowabe kawaama tiyeu co niiwo cam tureniri mari buwaro yobeu main nuwacuenti “"”  
\v 12 “Nawo bwetomage lowabe kwasma Burgsmssce mulangi birombo co ketito ki kulendo caca nyo yobeu,  
\v 13 “Min nyowom fiye muyintiyeu firen fiye kumja bwekele wiyeu. Kange wo gwamrn muntan denmiro kibi kwan, min nyimom mumabo——— bilen kerer kange mo, kikwama Antrfas nii bilenkerer, wo ne warke tiee, wuro cii twalum more kumeu, firn fice bwekeleu yimtiyem.  
\v 14 Dila dikeronwo ni nuwo lumacek kange mwen wonyo bi dunwi ti kangem tamki merngka Bilamu groingwinge, woci merang Balak nineu cin yoti diker kotangkar kabum Bibei Icirela wam, naciica carito cii tarbi briti wineu naci msten burotum.  
\v 15 Nyolak kangem kumembo tamki merangka niikolatawa gwriggurig.  
\v 16 lanswori kom dubam! Na munkori maan bou munen diber inma kwen kiyed kange cii tak ki kulen mor niyi miyeu.  
\v 17 Dila woki tuu nuwakan a cuwatuu dike yuwa fangbako yi lowabe kwaame tiyeu. wo cam turinri manneco manna yurangum yurangeu, mannecco tero fuworak kidend. fwir bulangum wi dok tevero wini dendowo kange nyombeu du'rkang miwo yoweu."””  
\v 18 Nawo bwetomange lowabe kawama Tiyatira muanyi wuro inco kefi mibwe kwaamero, wuro ki nuwe na biyen krrerui naniceu na kwerum kwereu.  
\v 19 “min nyemom diks mumeneu, rwika mwko, bilenkemweu kange nangen kange briom neve mweu min nyimow dike mumani kutangbeu la dike mumari ki kapa.  
\v 20 Dila dike maniri numa luma cekti kange mweu wo: yonentiw'u kange nawiyero yezebel wo co dorcevoti ki kimerang keceko ci'yama burotum ciya cacaritowo ciine bibwiti lumanereketak.  
\v 21 rim ne tureni co neci dudbom ci dobbo kange burotumcem bo.  
\v 22 To man merkerco kwanyri twaka, birombo ma burotum kange cotakeu ciywa dogen dotange dur, tans cidubo nangendo cii ma tiyevi nyim.  
\v 23 ma kra bibiyoloceu ki buwer, la lowabe kwaama kwawb an nyimom ruo rinfuwa dony dong nangen kumer.  
\v 24 La tangne kuweu ta ya tira, kwanub kume wuro tabo merang kako diker bwekelkero cuwav-kebo kange kori nri yitti miki nri yokumembo diker tutumer.  
\v 25 Kange wo nyo intamnyo komti kibi kwsn bou fiyati ko'mwi.  
\v 26 Wo cam turni kange wo dike nri maner yaken cwileri nyombo kwaama  
\v 27 Can ma liyar ce'vo ki dang nunyer, can wurongum cii na cer muret.”  
\v 28 Kamba rniyou Terimineu, mwo keneu mamneco britiren kwomcero.  
\v 29 Dilawo kituu nuwari acuws tuu dike yuwatamgbeko yi lobvqbe kwaamatiyeu.   
\c 3
\p
\v 1 “Ki bwe tomang'e lowabe kwaama sardisu mulangi: 'Biromboco ketito tam yuwa tangbetinim kwaamabo kange bitirendo “min nyimom dike mumaneu. munca den muke' mukidume wendi mun maniki dume.  
\v 2 Yuram ne bikwun nerer dike kumenin dilan dadom bwiyaka, wori mafi'ya naryen mwero diterbowi kabum kwaamau.  
\v 3 Law wori dubom, kidikero briombo muyo munuwau. Bwangten cii, dubom tati. Latano mu yurabori, manbomwen naniikuye, dila mani mu yurati kikwamawo mabomwenti kikiye'  
\v 4 Dila denti nubero wi sardisu nyo biduwar birombo kangbo kule ciryan yayam kange mo tw'kule do fuwor wori cii daten.  
\v 5 Wo man turiniri man dekcinen kulendo fuwortinin, marima wam denceroti mor bifumer dumer tak, mantok dencero tak kabum teemin, kange kabum wob tomangeb cebtak.  
\v 6 Ianaweu wuro tuuweri anuwa dike yuwa tangbe kayilowabe kwasma tiyeu."””  
\v 7 Ki bwe tomange lowabe kwaama mor filadelfiya mulangi; ketito briom wucak wo bilenke takeu-tamki nydo Daudu ko, ti woni mi nunka mani fiye ci nynnyeu niim owka mari.  
\v 8 Min nyiwom dike mu maneu. üo, minyo nyiloko wumom wume kabum mwem wuro nii womka maniye. min nyimom muuwi kibikwan biduwar, kangewuro gwam mun bwangten kerwiro mu mabo——- Denemiu.  
\v 9 To! mandok birombo yitiki ki ciin yafudawa lowabe bwekelkele Wendi cwerke cii cwertiye ciiya bou cii sungi narimwer, ciiyam nyimow mi cwinentitak.  
\v 10 Kambo mu bwam ner mor dangne mu bwangten wrefun rieu, mokeneu man ceerner kikiwamawo cuwerumbo ayira dorbitineroninti gwammeu, naccii cuwa nubo yim dorbitireu.  
\v 11 Mibouti wulom. Tam dike mu cikeu gwing gwing kati yilo kange tu mwen lalang duwek.  
\v 12 Niiwo man turiri man yokenco——————————— lowabe kwaarma miu, mani cacerti morecetak. Man mulang den kwaama wiro dorcer, den biten kwaamero (wurucahis fwir, wuro yiruti dii kwams fiye kwaams miwiyen), kange den miro fwirko.  
\v 13 Nawen wuro ki tuuweri anuwa dike yuwa tengbeko yi lorabe kwaawatiyeu."””  
\v 14 Nawo bwe tomange lowabe kwaama wo lawudikiya mulangi” Birombo co keti ati nyo, in frye bulauka kange nii ne warke bilanketiye, nii liyare dor dikero kwaawe fwele.  
\v 15 min nyimom dike mu maneu, mu yobbe mu cilongbo min cwi mu yiber kakaa cilon!  
\v 16 Dilonwori mun ——— cilon kebo yiber-mindador nn tumomner nyimi  
\v 17 Wori munyi muki, “Min nii cweka, minwi kidero kila mi cwibo diker buwer,” dila mu nyombo mu dirki—— diker buner nii bwini, fukmamukw anjertak.  
\v 18 Numo neka yulanek miko Tén mwindo minen wuro cii kwerum kikirau ne yilam mii cweka, na fiýa dubwimwenin kulendo fuwor birombo riblangti yeu katiyúo mudang kwanduwe kwanjere mweu, kange nuwang belti nuwe mwerin na mwati toi.  
\v 19 Mi mwe wuro micwitiyeti kwamb, ni merang ciinen kambo ciýa yim yim kalembo ti yeu lans wor,—— dubom.  
\v 20 To, rintin nyilo miti kwabi, tana kange nuwa dirmirori awuwom nyiloko, mandou mor loco, ḿca kangeco, cokeneu kange mo.  
\v 21 Wo cam turimiri, mantin dobco ci yi kangermo dor kutéler rir, kanmbo mo keneu má cam turini riyken kange teeḿ kutileceu takeu.  
\v 22 Lawo kituuweri anuwa dike yuwatangbeko yi lowabe kwaamatiyeu.”   
\c 4
\p
\v 1 Bwiko dikero bwro, min too, la nyiiloko dik kwama wumom-wume. Diro ki kaba ma nuwau, namwi namutun-mwen dike yii ti ki, “Bou fo dii nan nung mwen dike a bwiti kumeni weu.  
\v 2 kang dangchang mi mor yuwa tangbe, la min too kutile lúyare mor dii kwama, nii kange nyiim wi dor cher,  
\v 3 Nii wo nyim wi dor chereu, cherkang yasfa kange yakutu. kwang-yabe kentangum kutile liyare chuwo. kwang-yabe cherkang.  
\v 4 Kangum fiti nyim liyarem kumi-yob chulombo naar kentangum kutile liare wo, dor fiti yime buro, nobbo dur kwiri-yob chwhombo naar yiirongum wi ki kulendo fwor kange walbile liyabe milbangtiye chumangum dor chir.  
\v 5 Fiye kufite liyare wiyeu milbangka cheruu ti wi, diir dike wurongtiye kange kun-nye. Talkiretini nibeer ta kira ti kabum kutile liyare, tal kiretin yuwa tangbe kwaama nibeer.  
\v 6 Kabum kutile liyare nin wiima (gilache) wo tibati na (crystal) tiber kutile liyareu, kentangum wi kutile liyare, diker ki dume nyo naar bwam ka nuwe, bwii kange kab.  
\v 7 Dike ki dume kaabau, na turome, dike ki dume na yabe cheu na be nenne, dike ki chume na taare cheuwii ki tikob na nii fir, Ia naare cheu wii ki tikob na fiinge kwenti-kweneu.  
\v 8 Dike buro ki dume naareu, wirangi ki tangum nukikun-nukkun, bwam ki nuwe dii kange tob. kume kange kakuk, chi dobbo takka, “wuchak, wuchak, wuchak, teluwebe kwaama nii kibi kwang gwamme, cho wure, cho duwen, cho kabe.  
\v 9 Fiya chuwo dike buro ki dume ne duktongka, dur kange buka kangeke ri, nobbo durko wo kuni yob chulombo naaren, yarken bitine kabum nii wo yiim kutile liyare wab cho wo fuloti bak-ni-bakeu.  
\v 10 chi yoken wambile liyare chiweu kabum kutile liyare, takti ki,  
\v 11 laminye mo teluwe be kange kwaama be, yuwo duktong ka kange dur kange bikwan, mo ma ywel dikero gwamme, ki chiyaka mwe chi yime, chi ywelchiye.”   
\c 5
\p
\v 1 La min too kangko chattiyere nii wo yim kutile liyare, bifimer mulangum-mulange kab kange bwiko, bifimer mulangum-mulange kab kange bwiko, chrin kwati yrom liyam wi nibeer.  
\v 2 Min too bwe tomange kwaama wo kibi kwanne, kwa dirti kibi kwang, “We daten a wumom bifimero ti na kim yirombo chi kwatiye?  
\v 3 Nii mani dii kwaama kaka dor bifiner kaka mor bifie wo lam a wom bifimero ti kaka cha kiyerao dike more cheu.  
\v 4 Min chii wiiye chillen, wori ma fuya bo nii wo daten a wom bifimero na kiyerangu dike wiye.  
\v 5 La wiin mor nobbo dureu yii ye ki,”chiire wiye. Too turome dum yafuji, niiye Dauda ma turanni, cho cha wom bifumero kange yirombochi kwatiye”  
\v 6 Min too be kwame tim tiber fiyé kútile liyare wiye mor dikero buro ki dume naare, mor nobbo durko nin. mo too ri namwi chi twallum-twal. wi ki chume niber kange nuwe niber, wuro chi yuwa tangbe kwaama chi tomi gwam kale.  
\v 7 chon yá chon tuu bifumero mor kang nii wo yiim kutile liyare.  
\v 8 Kambo chitum bifumereu, dikero naar ki dumen kange nobbo durko kuri yobb chulombo naareu, yarkam bitine kabum be kwame, gwam chiye wirangi kibi benn kange kange kwele mwine dim ki kwaama ki kunn fichange, mwine dhilo nob kwaama wuchake.  
\v 9 Chin kaa nuwe ewir, “mon daten tuu bifumero na wumom yiro mbo chi kwatiye, chin biyem nen, ki bwiyale mwe mwa tiyen kwaama nin nobbe gwam olum, nyii kange kale.  
\v 10 mon ywel chú nob liyare kange nob wabeb na chi bwang kwaama ninten na chi liyar dor kaler.  
\v 11 Lamin too ri min nuwa dir be bei tomange kwaama duche wo kantgum kutile liyare, kange dike buro ki dume kange nobbo durko,  
\v 12 Kilaka chiyeko lam bikwate kwob kiritibikate kwob kange kiriti bikate, chin tokker ki diro dur “Lamiyeu mo be kwaame, wochi biyem ri yuwo bikwan, chweka, wicdom dwktongka kange ohaklangka”  
\v 13 Min nuwa dike chi fuli, dii kwaam, kange kale, kange mor kale kange wo dor wima, gwam dikero more chiye tokti ki, “Fiye nii wo yim kutile liyareu, fiye be kwame ninne, a ne chaklamka, dur, duktongka kange bi kwan liyaret bak-ni-bak”.  
\v 14 Dikero ki dume naareu tokki, “A ti nyo” la nobbo durko yarken bitie chin wab cho.   
\c 6
\p
\v 1 Minto ki kwamawr be kwame wumom win mordokka kangeko nibeereu, dils minuwa win mor birombo fwelfwele kidume naareu toki dir na diikwaama, “Bou!”  
\v 2 Lamator; minto; tuwa f; uwo;; r,;;; wuro yim wiyeu tamki cin neco lala duwektak. cin ceri turin naci ma turini.  
\v 3 Kambo bekwsme wom dokka kangeko yoberi, dila min nuwo dume fwefwele wo yobeceu yikii, Bou!”  
\v 4 La tuwa kange cerou kale-fiye kwiu. Dila nii kwikace ciin nemco kange ciya tum fuwor nervo dorbitiner, na nabceba twalamgum bwiticeu. Nii kwikakowo cii neco kulendo dur.  
\v 5 Kambo bekwame wom dokka kangeko taareri, iarnin nuwa dume fwelfuwe wo taarecu yikii, “Bou!” Minto tuwa fir, nii kwikaceka tamki bidigle cuwaka mor kangece.  
\v 6 Lamin nuwea nadiro kange mor biro fwelfuwe kidume naareu yikii, “Bidigle bikateu win yaka yiwkakukem, bidigle shair taartak. Dila kangre nuwengo kange mwembo twiber—-”  
\v 7 Kanbo be kwame wume dokko kangeko naarer min nuwo dir fwelkarowo kidume naareceu yikii, “Bou!”  
\v 8 Laminto tuwa kange Mwom bituwamen Nii kwiikaceko cii neco den buwar bwangfen cotitak ciin neco bikwan duret dor wumero naar wo dorbitineroceu ciiya twalangum ki kulen, wura, buwaratinim, kange nannagentindo kiyetak wo dorboitinerocu.  
\v 9 Kambo bekweame wom dokka kangeko nungeri, laminto dume nubo wuro cii twalanglum ke, kwaamareu cuga tanjdanek kange warko cii tabi takeu.  
\v 10 Ciin ciwiye ki diro dur, “Dilan fiy ang nii liyae gwamm, Nii bilenke kange wucakeu, mwan ma dubo yimror bitinernin bolang natum ceerka boiyale nyeko?  
\v 11 Dila krearubce ciinnecii kulenolofuwor lacii yitencii ciiys cobten ningtang biduwar tamo kilatum kebceb cangabo kebciibo nabarob kambo cii twalangum ciyeu.  
\v 12 Kanbo bekwame wumom dokko kangeko nukkunreri, mititoiri dila bikutakumyo dor wo bitine. kakuko yilam fije bwer wer na kulendo fiv, cwakko yilam na bwiyaletak  
\v 13 Bitiron diyeu yaruu bifine, kambo ti nyingjing nye tikam bitutti ce wuro birngbeu, tamo yuwako dur mokiri.  
\v 14 Dil kwamau lem na bifumero cii kumom kume. Bangtirimbo kange diiyele cii tungumco fiye ciwiyeu.  
\v 15 Dila liyabbo dorbitinereu kange nuboketimin kange liyal kweneb, nob cwekab, kange wob bikwanob, wori kange nubo wuyak, canga kange wuro friyam ceerkan cii yurangum mor bangtinim kange bidukletin.  
\v 16 ciinyi dukletinibo kange bangtinimbo, “kom yaruu dornyer! kutile liyareu kange funer be kwarnaro.  
\v 17 Wori kume funereco durko bou. we atiritiye?   
\c 7
\p
\v 1 Bwiyoko wori minto nob tomangeb naar cii tiri dor cungatinin naar wo dorbitineroceu, ciintam yuwoko naar wo dorbitinerceu gwingwing katiyil katiyilo yuwako fobi dor bitiner, dor wimar, kakaa tiyo kange.  
\v 2 Laminto niitomange yauti firen twar, wuro ki dokka kange dumek wo kwaama ceu. Cobi coro kidiro dur kange nob tomangabo wuro naar biro cii ciya ciinen ciya nere dor bitiher dortange kange wima.  
\v 3 “Kom nere dor bitinero, kange wimau dotange kange tini tano bi yoti dokka kange ko tikob kang'ab kwaama bekonind nyime.”  
\v 4 Lamin nuwa kalito biro cii dokum kangeui 144,000, birombo cii dokum kange mwanti nubo Israila.  
\v 5 Bikate kwob cilombo yab wo yahuza, Bikateu Kwob cilombo yob wo-mwanti Ra'ubainu, bikate kwob cilombo yob we-mwanti Gad,  
\v 6 bikate kwob cilombo wo yob wo-mwanti ashiru ceu, bikate kwo cilombo wo, Naftali ceu, bikate kwo cilombo yob wo-mwanti Manassaceu.  
\v 7 Bikate kwobcilom yob wo mwanti saminuceu, bikate kwobcilom yob wo-mwamti Lawicu, bikate kobcilombo yob wo mwamti Issaka ceu,  
\v 8 bikate kwobcilombo yob wo mwamti Zabalunaceu, bikate kwobcilombo yob wo mwamti Yusufuceu, bikate kwobcilombo yob wo mwamti Bilyaminuceu tak cii dokum kange.  
\v 9 Bwiyok dikerombori minto, laminto mwerkangkato dur wuro nii mani a kiyetiye cirang niffir mwamti, nob kange biyonti tirangum kabum kutile liyarem kabum be kwame. D urangum ki kulendo fuwor kange bilu debino kanciik,  
\v 10 cii cobicorti diir kibi kwan: “Fuloke kikwaama wuro yim dor kutile liyareu, kange be kwame tak!”  
\v 11 Nobtomangebo gwamm trirang'um kentang'um kutile liyare kentang'um nubo durembo tak kange nub dumebowo naar, ciin daken bitine. Kifwer kango tikobcibo kabum kutile liyare. Cii wab kwaama,  
\v 12 cii toki, Atinyo! caklangks duktangka, Dali, buka kangek, dwika, bikman duret, ciiyilam na kwaama bece yaken diri diri! Atinyo!”  
\v 13 Dila win mor nubo durembowo meye, “biwe birombo, durang'um kikulendo fuwore, cii ciroufe tak?”  
\v 14 Lamin yice, mi “mo nii dur, “mun nyimomye,” lanyiye, “Birombo cowo cirang'um cii yilamkico fuwor mor bwiyale kwame.  
\v 15 Won co duke bwi cii kabum kutile liyare kwaama cii wabcoti kume kange kakuk mor lowabece. Cowo yim dor kutile liyareu atin yilam bituk dorcir.  
\v 16 Mani ciya nuwaten wurati, kakoa dulomwe. Kakuk mani kwaciti, kakaa cilondowo twiti twiyeu.  
\v 17 Wori bekwame tiber kutile liyareu anyilam nii toka cel, ambwanten cicii yaken fiye mwem dumembo bwiti bwiyeu, kwaama atin wam mwemnumbo nuwece gwamin.   
\c 8
\p
\v 1 Kituremi bekwome mumom dokka kangeko nibereu, ciitam cine cin dikwama ne kangekenoke bidobe.  
\v 2 Dila minto nobtomangebo niber birombo tim kabum kwaamemen, ciin ne tencii cumen niber.  
\v 3 Kange nii tomange bor, kanki kwel mwine wo twiks diker nunne ceu, tiken kabum tangilanner. Diker twike nunko ducce ciinece naci neken war kange dilo nuba ne bilenketiyeu gwamm dor tangi lan twiks diker kuner wo mwineceu kabum kutile liyarem.  
\v 4 Yilom twika kunembo, kange dilotin wob neka bilinkere, cii kweni dii kabum kwaamam kange nii tomange.  
\v 5 Nii tomange co tu kwel twika kunneko dinco ki kira fiya tanjilando wiye. Lana nyime mouco bitine dor bitiner, dila kwaka kunnyekowo, kange kunnge kange miblangkako fuwo nyeu, kange jigtongka bitinektak.  
\v 6 NOb tomangebowuro niber birombo ki cumeni nibereu ciinkanuti cuka ceko.  
\v 7 Nitomange kaben cu cumeceu, labititen kwaamaronwo kange kirak ceikang'um kange bwiyale laciin mouc bitine to dorbitiner dila win mor taare dorbitinero twim, win mor taar wo tiniceu twim, kange uerako yiberko twim gwaam.  
\v 8 Nii tomange yobe cu cumeceu, dila dikeru durko kange certang ter wo tati tabe kikira ciin mouco mor wima. win mor taare wimau yilam bwityale,  
\v 9 win mor taare dikero kidume mor munge ciin bwiyam, la bitirendo tenang tenangeu yaruu dii, cati na kiro wenka, dor win mor taare wo cajiyoceu kange tiye bwika mungek.  
\v 10 Nii tomange yobeu cu cumeceu, la bitirendo tenang tenang'eu yaruu firen dii, tati nakira wenka, dor win mor dikero taar wo cajitinimbocen kange bwili mwen.  
\v 11 Denbitirenero twei, win mor taare mwem cajimbo yilam twei, dila nubo kila bwiyam wori mwemtinim be yilam twei.  
\v 12 Nii tomange naareu cu cumeceu, lawin mor taar wo kaku ceu diker kem, wim mor taare wokakuceu kange win mor taar wo bitirendoceu. La win mor taar wo ceu gwaam mmam kumtacile, win mor taar wo kakuceu kange win mor taar wo kumeceu cii lem filnciko.  
\v 13 Laka mitoweri laminuwa buyelangi tiber dii kwamareu cobicorti kidir kibi kwan, “Kaiton nubo yimdorbitinere wori tangni cume nobtomangebo wuro taaru ciya cutiye.”   
\c 9
\p
\v 1 Dila nii tomange nung'eu cu cumeceu. Minto bitirendo dii kwama yanu bou dorbitiner. Ciine bitirendowo nyilo nurekowo manikiyikau.  
\v 2 Wumom nyilo nurekowo maniki yikau, La yilombo cirou na yilombo buwak kirake diore. Kakuk kang yuwako yilam kumta cile, kiker yilomero ceruuti nyilo buwake ninneu.  
\v 3 Wi mor yilomein dila bikwake wo ciin ceruu bou dorbitiner, ciin neci bikwan nabi ningetinimbeceu mor dorbitiner.  
\v 4 Ciin yici ciyg nuware yeratimbonin kange biluwofir wiyak kakaa ti twirak, dilla kan nubo mani ki dokka tangek kwaamak tikaob ciibeu.  
\v 5 Cii necibo ciyaka ciiya twalum nubobiro, dila ciyanecii dotange na creakko nungece. Cilonciro tak anyilam buwak biningek no teniri.  
\v 6 Ki kumemiwo nubo ado buwaro, dila maniciya fiyacoti. Ciyanma kuru buware, dila buwaro an cwaci.  
\v 7 Bikwakeu cer kang tuwa cii tweng cii ywele. Dike kange wi na lalang duwek mwinek, tikob na niffiroce taki.  
\v 8 Yirir ciiro winyo na natuboceu, nunciiro nawo turomeceu.  
\v 9 Cii tirangiem ki sulke na kene tak, diir tangumacire na diir nabirer tuwar kwener kila nyeu yanu kwenemboci ywele.  
\v 10 Ciin wi ki yalak nyonglangi nabi ningetinimboceu, ciin wi kibi kwan yalak ciikonin na ciya nemnubo dotangeti na cwakka nungece.  
\v 11 Ciin wiki kange naliya dorciir, nii tomange buwakko maniki yika. Dencero ki Ibrancin Abadon, Ki Helengnci ri Afoliyon.  
\v 12 Kabako cum. Tobwiyok wurokiri wi nye yob birombo boutiyeu.  
\v 13 Nii tomangu nukkuneu cu cumeceu, dila min nuwa diir cumero tangilan mwinero kabum kwaamamem.  
\v 14 Diro yil nii tomange nukkuneu tanki cumeu, “Kwim nobtonmangebo biro bwam caji yufiretis”.  
\v 15 Nobtomangebowo naar ciiyo na kangken woceu, kange kakuko wuro kange cwakka wo, kange coro wuro tak, ciin nyamkang ciinen nacii twalum win mor taare niffere.  
\v 16 Kilaki nob dakebo dor tuwareu inco 200,000,000. Min nuwan kilaka ciika.  
\v 17 Nyo mato tuwea tirimbo mor dukumeri kange no kwika ciibo tirang'umki sulke cii fiye kwiu na kira, fir shudi kange mwem birenem. Dor tuwar tinimbo nyonga gelbatinimboceu, nyicenin kirak, kange yilom kange kirako fuwor cirang'um.  
\v 18 Cii twalum win mor taare nube sulusin yan'adam wo taareu kirak, kwen kange kirako fuworko cirou nyiciyeu.  
\v 19 Wori bikwan wo tuwatinimbo nyiceu kange yalaktinimbo ciimbo-wori yalaktinimcimbo cerkan nacuwetin, ciinwi kidortak wo cii nuwa nubonin twirakti ciken.  
\v 20 Tangre niffiren cii twalbo ki-balai weu, cii dobbo nangendo cii maneu. Cii dobbo bwanta kelkelibo kange ninga mwineu, kange. Kange tagulla kange ter, kange ti-dikertinimbo mami tor, nuwa, kakaa yayam.  
\v 21 cii dobbo maka nangeu kuyet ciiro tak.   
\c 10
\p
\v 1 Dila mintokange nitomange yauti fiven dii kwama cumom cume mor bilore, kwangyabeu wi dorcer Tikobcebo no kakau, natirimcembo na ——— kirak.  
\v 2 Tamki bifumero biluware kamcek, lacii wumir, diladokti naceko cattiyero dor wimar, naceko mokeu dorbitinertak.  
\v 3 Dilan kwakiygngeu kidiro dor na tirme yam ciitiye. kituren cii kwo kiyangeu, dikreams biro nibecreu tok ker kange kiyange ceu.  
\v 4 Kambo dikwamabiro tokkereri, mikwicik kange kange mulangka, dila min nuwa diro kange diikwama ki, “Tam yurka dikekowo dikwamawo nibeer yineneu mulangcore;  
\v 5 Dila nii tomangewo rito tim dor wimar kange bitineu, kung kangceko cattiyero dii kwama.  
\v 6 Lan warum kangewo kiduwe diri diriyeu-wo fwel dikwsmau kange dikero worece gwsmes kange dorbitinero kange gwamr dike dorceru, kange wima kange dike gwamm moreceu, diks rii tomangeu yiki,” tabka bwiyeko kange main.  
\v 7 dile diye rii tomange wo nicowyurks kwaamako adimtiye, dong dong nawo ciyi amgabceb nob tomangob dukumeb.”  
\v 8 Diro rinuwa dikwamau token ker kange mo;” yaker, yatu bifumerowo wuwon wume kang nii tomange wo tim dor wimar kange dor bitinereu.”  
\v 9 lamin yaker rii to mangerin rinyico ri neye biffumero biduwareu. yiye ki, “tu bifumero cam Andok fwermwero yilam twei dila nyimweru antwibi na yuti.”  
\v 10 Mintu bifumero biduwareu kangrii tomangekeu min cam twibi kambu kan nyimi na yuti, dila twer, la fwermiro yilam twei,  
\v 11 kange yiye ki, “intam nyo mwam token ker dukumer tak kange ducce, kange riiffir kange bitenti kange liyabtirim.”   
\c 11
\p
\v 1 Ciin neyi dang nyone kwel cuwaki diker inmannangeu ciko. Ciinyiyeki, “kweri cuwam lowabe kwaamcu kange tangila do kange bŕrom ma waberti moreceu.  
\v 2 Dila cuware cungani lowabe, wori ciinneken nubo nyombo kwaamsu. cii yan fuwarrangúm cinararo wucakkeu na cwakko kwini naar culombo yobe.  
\v 3 manne waikeb mibu yob bikwam naret ciiya tokker dukurmer na kumeri bikatewin kange kwin kwim kwob yob toro kwini nukkun, dumki fiti kulere.  
\v 4 Warke bŕmboco timi-zaitun ne yob kange talkire yobtak tirangum kabum taluwe dorbitinere.  
\v 5 Tano kange dangi can nuwa cirendi, kira miko ceruu nyicii ciiwam mob kiyeb ciibo. Tano niwo criiti naci nuwa ciinenar, intam nyo ontwaluumco nurewo.  
\v 6 Warkebo birom wiki bikwan neret naci kum diikwamau kati yilo mwembo kikwamawo to tokker dukumerotiyeu. ciiwn kibi kwan neret dok mwemtinimbo yikan bwiyale, cii kwale dorbitineriwo tak ki balai —- ki kwalen cii cwi yeu.  
\v 7 Kambo cii dim worko cori, Atrican tureidorcir twalumci.  
\v 8 Bilentinim ciimbo andarangken dor nurer cinslor durkowo(wuro dangi cicoti ki saluma kange masareu) frýe cii kulken teluweceu.  
\v 9 Kikume taar kange bidoberi fiye nubo wiyeu wiyeu kwawb, kange mwamtor, kange biyen kange mren nuber cii yaanto bilentirin cimbo. cii yanko dokka ciiko mor tuwe.  
\v 10 Nubo yim dorbitinereu ciiyam fuwa cika dorcer. ciyatin twon bwiticenin luma nerek wori nob tomangebo wuro yobeu nuwa nubo yim dorbitinerenin  
\v 11 Dila ki kuwe taar kange betbri, fuborn dumen fiye kwaama wiyeu andou worece lana nyime ciiyam tidor nacer. Tari kamboken anbo nubi tocii tiyenin.  
\v 12 lana nyime ciiyam nura dir kibi kwon diikwama yiciti, ko kwiufo!” lana nyime ciyan yaken dii kwama mor bilore, nob kiyeb ciiyeb titoi.  
\v 13 ki kwamaco anma mikaka bitinekodur, dila win mor kwobe cinalooro forum. Nubo bikate niber anbwiyam mikaka bitinuekonin, biro fulomeu amcwamtai ciine kwaama diiyeu duktangka.  
\v 14 Balaí wo yobeu cum To! bala'i taareceubouti nawo nawo.  
\v 15 Lana nyime niitowange nibereu cu cumeceu, dila dirtinimbo ciya ciyau tokker dikwame ki, “Liyarodor bitineru yilam liyar teluweber kangewo Almaciyaceceu. Anma liyaro diri drir.”  
\v 16 Lana nyime nubo durembowo kwini yob ciyobmbo naar yirongum kutile liyaretinim cem kabum kwaamoun, cip yari tikobciibo bitine. ciwab kwaama.  
\v 17 ciiki, “nyin bu mwenkang, Teluws kwaama, Niidukangka, wuor naweu kange wour nanduweu, inwori muntu bikwan ner, dila funer mwero munter liardo.  
\v 18 Mwanubero ciin kangun ner, dila funer mwero bou. Tureniu bou nawo ciiyama buwanin bolangti yeu, wo mwane bebai cungab mwebo nobtomangeb dukumer, kange nob bilenkereb cuner týe, kange birobo cwatai dener mwereu, biduwareu kange durko Tureri lam nawo mwa mvongum birombo wurongum dorbitirnerotiyeu.”  
\v 19 Lana nýme wumo lowabe kwaama firen diyeu, na nyime to kwelbiye noreceu mor lowaberece. dila miblangka filangeko, kange ——— diikwama, kange mikaka bitinak, kange ternti bititer kwamar.   
\c 12
\p
\v 1 La to kange dang ke duk wi di kwama. kange nawye ehumom aorr cher ki kakowk” la kange wi mor nacheng. la duwe bitrome. kob chollomro yob wi yom doe cher.  
\v 2 Cho wi kii fwer, cho wi chiwiyet, ker bworum bwem mor dotange bore.  
\v 3 Di la chon to kage duk mor li kwama. To, kange wi dukna chuwe fiyeze kange chumeni kwabila myo wo kurendo ni ber wi lortinimbo  
\v 4 Yalang cheko cho tom win mor taar wo bi trene che di kwama choru cho bitiye. Nange Dur wo tii kabum nawiyembo wo dadum boka chano ki kwama cho bommeri na cho wuhum bi bwe che.  
\v 5 La chon boo bwe, bweule, woo a ma liyar no bertiye gwam ki dange ki yemek, chi chwabrum bwe chúu choko kwaina chu nin kutule che.  
\v 6 Nawiye ohwa chu yeran fiye kwama ywel ohinene la na nyom ki cho kuma 1,260.  
\v 7 Cho kwama chorocho kwani di kwama mikalu kange nob tomange che chi teh kwen kange nob tomange chi ma kange chi eni.  
\v 8 Di la diragw man kibi kwan wo cha cham kaba tiye lanyo, cho kange nob to mange che fiya bo fiye di kwama.  
\v 9 La chi merken diragon warige kange nob tomange bitine la na chiiwe charko chuwo ki bwekelkele wuro bolang no boti fo kale weu.  
\v 10 La mo nu wa kange dik ki bi kwan di kwama chaneu cherka biye ken, bikwan, kange liyar kwanaber kange i kwan na almachiya. kambo chi merken nii toka nah kebben bitine cho nii wiiro cho torang chi ti kabum kwama kume kange kakuk  
\v 11 Chi cha kaba kange cho ki bilencne cher, kambo chi chwibo, Du me chiyeu yaken chiko bwar.  
\v 12 Ta Nyor, ma forner, kam no bo diyen kange ciwam no yim more chiyeu dila bwiram bro kaleu kange wima ki den bwerelkele wo yirau kimeneu no dimki funere bwireu, kambo chonyomom kumeni che kum bi dombe.  
\v 13 Kambo diragon to chi merken cho bitine cho chi kwamchang Nawi ye wuro bo bwebi bare.  
\v 14 Kambo chi ne mawi ye wunro takkuum yob naliye dure che na cho chwa cho chull fiye chi ywel chinen wi kre. cho fiye chuno chi ya to cho ti bekumen; Kange kumeni kange kwama  
\v 15 Na chuwe kwiu mwem bo nyi cho nii chaci dige bwiyeu na ñwa lum cho.  
\v 16 Dila bitineu tikang na loiyeu, bitineu wu mom nyi cheu min chu chiyo drangondo knriwu nyi chenineu.  
\v 17 Di la drag omdo ma funer kange nawiyeu, chin chu ya nhom ma gwer kange ma biringe kange ker kwama yi lo chi tam ki bilengre ki den yeecu.  
\v 18 La drangon nya ti dor yabum, wi kabam wi mam.   
\c 13
\p
\v 1 La nyo ma to kange Nmige ki ye cheruti wi chaji, wi ki chumeni kob kange doro niber, wi dor chumechinin biduli ngdule kob, wi dor chumenin dendo wi ki dendo bwir.  
\v 2 Bi chiro wuro man to wi nyo na naweh natinm chebo wi nyo na bitolo nyi che na nui trome i dirangon wo cho bikwan chero bikwan dur li yareche.  
\v 3 Win wi mor dorem bi cho, la der chero Bwir chero bim, di la kalewo chi to nyimang ka ki kwama chi bwanten bichiro tiye.  
\v 4 Chi kene chi ne diracion dur, na cho ne durko durchero. chi ne durko chi tokti ki we na durko! we tank adol maka kiyankti kange he?  
\v 5 Chi ne durko nyi wuro cho tokker ti na kunka doreko che kange kero bwikna cho fiya bikwan tokka kereng yaken kume kwini na'ar chulon boyob.  
\v 6 Dila bichnro wom nyi cheu tikang kero bwirti dor kwamak chwekang Den cheroti kange fiye nyi che kange noboro yim di kwama.  
\v 7 Chi chiya durko nin wo ma kwen kange nob kwama cho cham kaba kange chi, cih necho bikwan nai yank tinimbo nin, kange no ber.  
\v 8 Gwam nobo yim to kale we chi ta ne cho bidwiyer gwam noboro ki kaka fwwlka kale chi mulang bo dentichero mor bifumerna be kwame che wuro chi biye.  
\v 9 No kange wi ki tupu ki wori cha nhwa cwam nii wuro chi tuu cho ti yati ki cho fiye changa cho yatiye.  
\v 10 Gwam nii wo chi ya twal cho ti ki kulene, kulen chi twal cho ti chike kulen chi twal chotiye wuro cho bicha wa kale cheu, birum ner kange bilenke wi ni boro wuchakke.  
\v 11 La mo to kange, bichir wi che ru ti wi mor bitine. wi ki chume yob cherkang bekwame che yolo chon tokker na na chuwe che.  
\v 12 Cho mw atum Dur bikwan gwam bichir kaba kabum chem di la cho dok kale kange nobo yim wi yeu chi ya ne bichir kaba dur wuro chi twa chimen twira tamwi na bware che.  
\v 13 Ma dur bwa yilener cho dok kirako yirau bitine dikwama kabum no bem.  
\v 14 Wa dang dike chinene cho mane, chon bolang nobo kale chon yi chi ya ma yirom kange ki der kulene di la na chuno bum.  
\v 15 Chi chiya chimen cha ne fubom dor urom bichronin, naurom bo na tokker, cha dok chi ya twallum gwam nii ko neka bi dwiyer bichironine.  
\v 16 Cha tok dige tamme, nobo gwam bidwurtinim kange durtinim nobo chuve chuyeu kange nob bwinem no mabwiti ki change kangehiwke chi ya yirom kan chick kange tikob.  
\v 17 Mani a math yo Lange nii wo manki numbari Mani can ten keneti, keneceu ki nang na dencer.  
\v 18 Wuro ki chwi yiien no nii kange wi ki yiien di cha ki yem kilatum bichior wuro. kilatum na nii fire che. kilatumbo cho wo 666.   
\c 14
\p
\v 1 La man to bekwame tim dor bang chiyona wari kan-nge chonubo wii bikatewin kwini kwob nar turo nar che, buro chi mulang den chi re kan-nge der techere tikob chiyeb.  
\v 2 Man nuwa dor kang-nge chiyati na dir mwenger chaji chwati kang-nge kunnye kwatiye. Diro ma nuwa cherkan nob gilingili-nge chi kwa gilingili-nge chiyeti.  
\v 3 Chi ka nuwe fwir kabum kutile liyare kang-nge kabum fule wo kwareche nare kang-nge nubo durtinimbo. kang-nge mani wo tiye, la kan nubo 144,000 wuro chi fan-ngu chi dor bitinere.  
\v 4 burombo chi wuor chi mam bo kayaka wi kang-nge natubed; la chi warum dur chiyero wuchak kang-nge mulen daunkuram. wuro cho bwawer bekwameti gwam fiye cho ya wiye, chi wo fan-ngu mor nube na chi yiam bilca kabak kwama kang-nge bekwame.  
\v 5 Chwerke uyambou nji, chi man ki duti.  
\v 6 Man tô bwetomange wucchake kang-nge kweni tiber dii kwama, wo ki fulen do bak lumi nyeu, a yi dorbitinerotiye, na wo a yii bertinimbo ti gwamme kang-nge nyini, kang-nge nubo.  
\v 7 Cho bichor ki diro dur, kom nuwa tai kwama, kom ductang cho. la bolang chelco lam. wabcho, cho wo ma diiko kang-nge bitine, kang-nge wima, kang-nge wuchak, bwetoman-nge wuchake wo yobe che, bwa-ngu yiti ki, yarum babila, babila durko yarum, wuro bol nubo irko gwan a nôô mwen bitutti tiye burotum cheme.  
\v 8 ka-nge betoma-nge kwentiniim bwetoman-nge wuchwce WO yobe che, bwa-ngu yiti ki yarum babila durko yarum, euro bol nuto firko gwan a nōō muen bitutti tiye burotum cheme. kan-ngu chi ki Dirk kuean Keane, yiti ki nawo wab bichir do wo nii kang-nge fulen chereri, yo kulang kangchek kalca tikobchekeri.  
\v 10 Cho ken chan nōō mwca bituti funere kwang, mwen bitutti WO chi choir chan chak mor kwel funere che, WO no no cheri chiyan necho dotang-nge ki Kris, kang-nge kriako fuwor, kabum nubo wuchak biboi to man-nge kwama kang-nge bekwame.  
\v 11 Yilom dotang-nge chiye to kweni dii diri-diri, take chi mankind fobka kume Lange kalck-buro chi nubo chi wab bi chirp Lange dubi che, Lange gwam buro yo yirom dene che.  
\v 12 Euro chi bichor bika mwirumka burombo wuchakke, buro bwamten werfuner kwamara ki bilenke mor yechi.”  
\v 13 Man nuwa bi chirp dii kwama yiti ki mulang wo, nob bibwiyer nobo bwiyam bwiya wo bwiya mor Teluwer yuwatangbeko wuchakke yii ki long work chin fubom kang-nge dotang-nge chiye, di la nangen chiyero bwang chinenten.  
\v 14 Ma tori biloro fuorko wo. him biloko nine tamwi bibwenifire. wiiki nēēduwe Maine dorcher kang-nge bilore wo cha bye kangchek.  
\v 15 Do kang-nge bwetomange wuchakke cheri bikur wabker, chi bi cho bi chirp kibi tūū bilor mwe yoten kang biyeka bito ko wuro kini biyeka bitoko dorbitinero lam.  
\v 16 La wo him for bilore mobken bilore che dorbitiner, la biyen dorbitineo.  
\v 17 Kang-nge bwe to mange wuchake cheri mor biker saber feren dii kwama, cho kene wiki bilore cha bye.  
\v 18 Kang-nge bwetomange wuchake cheri tanjila twita nuwang fichanger wo with ki bi kwan aber kirer. cho bi chirp ki dior kwamkwame wuro rin tankî bilore cha-nye, tūū bilore mwe cha-nyeu mweru bitutti mabi tii Mani wo dorbitiro n'm, mabi BIM”  
\v 19 Bwetomange wuchake met bilore che, mweru bitutti mabi dorbitinere chorkeu mor tale due wo chi yamum mwen mabi finer kwamar.  
\v 20 Chi fuwarangum fiye yanka bitutti mabi bwim chinanlor bwiyale chuati fiye yamka bitutti mabi, land NGO na duka nyi tuwak, yaken Mel Kai kwob yob.   
\c 15
\p
\v 1 Man Tó kange yirum dii kwama Tenangi ne yumanka; Bibei tomange wuchake niber ki fenjange niber, wo cho fenjange chwabire, ki cho funer kwamaro a diitiye.  
\v 2 Man Tó dike fiya na cher kanguweu nyo na chaji nuweturome tibati mwer kangum kange kira. Tim kangchaji chi nubo ki trini dor biyuwaro kange cher kang ka chek kange kulangko nung denchere. chi ka nume musa, chan-nge kwama, kange nuwe békwame; Nan-nge muero ka dur ne nyumankati, Té kwama, ni bi kwwane gwam wuchak kam-nge bilenke nure mwe. liya nubo fire.  
\v 3 Wé mari a nuwa tai mwe tiye téé, nacho dukteug den mwere. Wori ka mó winchwor wo wuchake. Nobo nyombo kwama chiyam bo kabum mwen ci wabnen, wori naangen mwero fwetangiwuchak.  
\v 4 We mani a cwanentiye Teluwe, na chaklang dimwereu? Mo ki kwamo mun wucak. Kalewo gwam ciya boy na was men na nimde mo, na wo cakcake.  
\v 5 zwiko dige wurombo ma tó, bi kur waber warka dii kwama.  
\v 6 Fiye wuchak wuchake, bibei tonange wuchake niber buro tamki fenjage riber chhin bó. chi mera-ngum ki kulen do wuwake kan-nge yuanko chumer wo tiba nyeu, chi chakka-ngum changchang chiyeko ki mwin.  
\v 7 Win mor fuléwo nar kwache né bibei tomange wuchak ni bere tacha mwine niber olinki funer kwamar wo kwarche diri diriyeu.  
\v 8 Bkur wabero dir ki yilom duktang ka ih wama kange bikwan cher. ka-nge man a dol dokachecki, fenjange riber wo bibei toma-nge wuchak nibere diminme.   
\c 16
\p
\v 1 Man nuwa diro dur co bicor mor ku wabe yi nobtomange wucakeu, ko ya ko coru niber wo funer kwamaro ceu dor bitiner.  
\v 2 Nii tomange wucake kabau yam coru dike mor kwewa ceu dor bitire, detiyo bwira-bwirau twirmangteneu bou mbo brombo ki cami bisirereu nubo wuro wab frle cereu.  
\v 3 Nii toange wulakeu yobeu yan coru ce dike mor kwelya ceu mor wima yilam bwiyale na bwiyal nii mmyame, la dikebor ki dume coru dike kwelya ceu mor canjiyaramgeum.  
\v 4 Nii tomange wucakeu tareu coru dike kwelya ceu mor canjiui kange kwenti mwenge la yilam bunyale.  
\v 5 Man nuwa nii tomange wucakeu mwemen,” To ki mon nii dong-donge. mo na wo mo nonduwo; wori war bocangko dong-dongeu.  
\v 6 Wri cin cor bwi-yale wab dukumeb mwebo kange mbo bwangtere ti wucakeu. mon he ci bwiyale ra ci nom dike daten kange ciye.  
\v 7 La man nuwa tanjilando wucakeu kare, ong tewwe kwama nii bikwane bwolang mweko dong dong. bilenke.  
\v 8 Nii tomange wucakeu Nareu corn dike mor kwelya ceu dor kakuked, lan ciya ciren twirang nubo ki kira.  
\v 9 cin twira aĺereko wo kirako twicitiyeu cin nng dikaka ki den kwamar nii kibikwan dor cotireroweu. la ci yilo tenbo na ci re kwama dur.  
\v 10 La nii tomange rungeu, coru dike mor kwelya ceu dor fiye yime bisireu, la kumta ciliu ciyam liyar cero, ci kirong biyenti cciyeroti ker alener.  
\v 11 Cii too kwama nii diko ki ker twirero kange detito, duwal ryeu cin ko ra ci y'uaten die bor ci matiyeu.  
\v 12 Nii tomange wkkureu coru dike mor kwelya ceu mor caji durko yufiretus, mwemcem kuicim, ra ywelum nnre wo liyabo bro yauti nutuwa a domtiyeu.  
\v 13 Man to yuwa kelkeliko taar wo cerkang bilareu cerauguti mor nyiye bwekl kelerin, kange biciro.  
\v 14 Cin yuwa kelkelik ci manang dike myumankaro kila kilau. cin cen ciki yam liyabo kila-kuanin dor bitirero wo ra mwermm ci fiye win na ma ka kwereko ce kakmk kwamko duko.  
\v 15 “ To ii ma bou na niikwiye, nii bibwi-yereco nii yimki batiyeu. dum ki kulen cer, ia mani ca certi kwenjer ra to kwanjer cero.  
\v 16 cin bou ki ci fintange coti ki armagidoneu kiryi ibrariya.  
\v 17 Nii tomange wrcake nibereu coru dike mor kwalya cen dor yuwar, la diro durko kange cern mor ku wabe kaange fuyeti yi toki-”Dim.”  
\v 18 Lan ma miblanka, kange mukaka bitinek, mukka knwu la tangnim bo ro mammanre wiyeu fiyaco bi bwe rifer yim dor bitimeru, makakko ra dur.  
\v 19 Cinam loro durko kabkangum more taar, ciman dur wab kumta cilibo yamm. la kwama kwaki Babila durko, la re cinan loro corin mwem tiyem bo dim kweleu wo ma ki funeer kwamareu.  
\v 20 Diyele diramum, la bangtimmbo mari t ti tak.  
\v 21 Biteten kwaman dwko turongi riyeu yarangu dii dor mmber, la cin tookwama ker cotire teten kwamaro wori tetendo nerci dotange.   
\c 17
\p
\v 1 Win mor nob tomange wucak nikbereu bro tabangum ki kwalyatimm mbiru, bou yi ye, man mwen warka bulongeko durko wo mwati nawye burtume wro yim dor meemtimm bo kila-kila nineu.  
\v 2 Kange co liyabo dor bitinereu ma bwiratum tiye ki nyom burotum cembo yorbeu, dok mbo yim dor bitineren wo masti.  
\v 3 La nii tomange wucakeu, tu ye mor yuwa tangbek yaken ki mo mor kiye, la man to nawiye yim dor bisirero fiyer dimri denti dilakar. bisiro co wi ki doiro riber kange sume ri kwob.  
\v 4 Nawiye comerum ki kulen do yiwe kange-fiye cin cor cinen mwin kange tetendo mwin kange tetendo ki kiyemereu. co tam ki kwelmwenge mwine dimki kulen burotumer kange bwiratum kil-kila. kange duti brira tumeceu.  
\v 5 Tikob ceb den mulangum wi ki yurke. “Babila durko” Nee nos burotumed kange dike bwira dor bitiuereu.  
\v 6 Ma to nawiye co nom briyale nubo bwang kwama rin tiyeu ma to coti kange rubo ci twali ker den yeecureu, kambo matoce ri la man nyumangi ki bi com.  
\v 7 la nii tomange wucakeu me ye, ye bwimo nyumang tiye? man yi ren yurke nawiyeu kange bisiro wo tuceu, bisiro wo ki dotiro riber kange cumeri kwobeu.  
\v 8 Bisiro wo mo to kwattiyeu, mari can, darom a ceruti-mor buwarke cuwau, la can yakan twalan ka. Nubo yim dor bitinereu, ki kulka dor bitinereu. ci an nyuma ngi na ci tobisiro wo wi kwatti mani can, la da-dom bouka.  
\v 9 Bisor wo ki mbo wo ki yulaneu, doro ribereu bangtini niber wo niber wo nawieu yim dor cire.  
\v 10 Cin liyab niber tak, liyabo nung yargum, kum win catiye, wineu la bo bouti, la na bouri ca ti na kumtium bo bidobece.  
\v 11 Bisiro wi kwatti, na wo maniyeu, con liya naraubeu, coki wo kange brombo ribereu  
\v 12 Cumei wo mo to kwobeu liywab kwob wo ba yo ci bo yo buri, la ci ar yo bikwando na liyabe ciyeu ra kang kereko wine kange bisiro.  
\v 13 Neerciyero wir cin neker liar ciro kange bikwan ciyero bisiro ni.  
\v 14 Ci am tekwen kan be bar kwameu, la be bar kwame am cam liya liyabe la war kange co ci bro cocoweu, cok-cokeu kange wob bilenker.  
\v 15 Nii tomange wiicokeu yi ye, mwembo wo mwa toen ro nawúye burotume yim dor cereu, nob mwerkako kilo-uẃa bitenni kange njini.  
\v 16 Cumeri m'ber wo mo toweu-ci kange am ko nawiye burotumeu. ci an kwinco na to kwanjer cero ci an narge ceu ci an twim co ki kira gwam.  
\v 17 Wori kwama yoti reer cirger na ci ma dike co cirye ki ciyaka cek, na ci rener bikwan liyare ciyero bisiro nin, ker kwamaro dim rimre.  
\v 18 Nawiye mo toweu cocinamloro dirko ki bikwan a ta liyabo dor bitinero tiye.   
\c 18
\p
\v 1 Bwiko dige burombo gwam, man to bwetange wuchakke kang-nge yirauti dii kwama. wi ki bikwando dut kambo ken, dorbitnero tiba ki dwamgka chek.  
\v 2 Cho bi chor ki chiro kwamkwame ki,” yarum, Babila tenaginye yarum! yilam fiye yime kelkelib, kangye fiye mwerangka yuwako bwir  
\v 3 Nubo gwam nom mwen inabi burotuwchenbo cho. Nob chwekako olorbitine chi chwen kibi kwan chika cher fenjange che fiya kom.  
\v 4 “Di ma nuwa chiro kang-nge kwama yi ki, “kom cheru more che, nobmoib kom more bwirangke na chiye, kari ferjange che fiya kom.  
\v 5 Bwiranke chiye mweri cweri lam dii kwama bulangi nand-ngen lam bwira yeu.  
\v 6 Lom ya chunero dong dong nawo cho ya ka-ngembo nine, kom ya cho kiriti yob kambo cho mane, mor kwele cho dawwe kom dal chinen kiriti yob  
\v 7 Nawo oho kun dor cherotiye cho chatika chila che, kom ne cho dotang-nge kalaka kang-nge fir rer nyo. Wori chom toki mor nere che “ma yim na liya, maa kebo nawiye bune, mani ma yii kangbuwati.  
\v 8 La nyori fcujange che kakuk win a fiya cho tiye, bwar, kangbuwa kang-nge wura. kira an twin cho wulak, wori iee kwama nii bikwane, kang-nge wo warchinen bwolange.  
\v 9 Liyab dorbitinero ma burotumeu, cii ti yangumten ciko takeu, cii yam ciwiye kange wiye buwo dorcer kambo ciito yilam twita cekemberi.  
\v 10 Cii yam ti firen kutam cii cwatai dotangero ki “Kwanne, kwan cinaloro dur, Babila ciialor bikan liyaret! wori warkaceko bou cikowin”  
\v 11 Nob miyaka dikerko durembo dorbitinereu ciiya ciwiye kange fir nerefkercer, kambo niikange main teredor yor yoreu  
\v 12-13 Kulen mwiner, Azurfa, kange terndor yoryoreu kange dike yiliuweu, kange lalango cumer, kange lalam tibaka kange tiyo ki kun twam twani, kange kulendo cii cwe ki tiyo fafa, kangewo kemero twaba twabaceu, kangewo kemero kucerko ceu, kangewo ter—— kange mwembo twiber kange nuwang, kange rúm bikatem, kange bikate, kange nena, kwame, kange nubetin. kange keke tuwa, kange changab, kange dume nifiretinim.  
\v 14 Charito kiyeu mu yoten nerroi kange bikwamwi gwam cii cerum munen. mwekor ciin lem, marri afiyacitiak.  
\v 15 Nob miyekabo durembo wo kulendo biromdoceu cii cwecikeu, ciyati firen kutanghi kange co, ker cwaka dotanyhencek, wiye kange wiye buwa fir neret.  
\v 16 Ciiyam toki,” kwanni, kwan chinaloro durko wuro dumki; lalanko twiya twiyau kange kulendo yilieu yiliuweu kange lal; ang tibakako fiyertak, wocica duka ki kul; en mwereu, kange terendo yoryoreu kange kulen bwayil; enner!  
\v 17 Mo; r kirri win cwekako; wn yakam.; wuyak nubof; u jirgi mungge tiyev,; kange nubo; no; b kwikabo; kange nubo fubýev kange birom fiýa kutangi.  
\v 18 Ciici wiyev kambo ciito yuomtrika cembem, ciiki,”: wuro cinalor incerka cinalor coka.  
\v 19 Ciinreati kwero dorcer, ciinciweyeu kibi twan, kange wiye buwa kange fir neret, “Kwari, kwan cinal; or wuro ǵirǵi... munfe fiys cweka wiyev wori kin kini win cii dimkangece”  
\v 20 Kom ma bitangtum dorcer, fuwor neret, kom nubo nebilenketiyev, nobtomangob, kange wobtomangab dukumeb, wori kwaama bouki warkako dorcer?”  
\v 21 Nii tomange tenangtenange tu tero cerkar ter kuwaska nerek, merkenco mor moremme titoki ki, “kinco nurewo, babila, linalorodur an merkenco bitine kibi kwan, mani atotencotiak.  
\v 22 Dir nubero kwabibentiyeu, nuboka nuwetiyeu, nubocu liranktiyeu, kange nubo biro cu.............. mani anuwsten ciiti more cetak. Unw ango kange mani kange twari................... wo afiys morece mari anuws dirr kuwaaka nevekti wi morecetak.  
\v 23 Filang takiretko mari cwobten reka filangekti morece. mari anuwa dir nii birnerti kange binne morece, inwori............ incii bábei nubo ma liyan dorbitinerotiye, mor.................... mwa bolnubo take.  
\v 24 Morece ciifiya buyal wobtomangeb dukumebe kange nubo ne bilenke, kange buyal nubo ciitwd dorbitinere gwari.”   
\c 19
\p
\v 1 Bwiko dike tinim buro ri man nuwa diro kange wo cerkang dir nubo ducce dii kwama cii tok ti ki, “halliluya, fuloka duk tangka, kange bikwan na kwama be ce.  
\v 2 Warke ceu bilenke ri cwika duwe mani, wori cin warker nawiye dor burotume durko wo kangum dor bitiner ro ki burotum cem me. Cin yam nando co ki bwiyale canga tini ce wo co nanwiye ki burotume coreu.  
\v 3 Ciin tok ker owo yobe ceu. Haliluya yilombo ceru cinen bak-nin bak.  
\v 4 Nubo dur tinimbo cilombo naareu kange dikero wo ci fweli ki dume naareu ciin yarken bitine cii wab kwama, wo yim dor kutile liyareu. Cii tok ti ki “Ati nyo, Halliluya!”  
\v 5 La diro ceru kutile liyare nin tok ti ki “Caklang kwama be, kom canga tinni ce gwam, kom nubo ko cwa tiye, nubo ki bi bikwan lkiyare kange wo man ki kibi bikwan liyareu,”.  
\v 6 La man nuwa diker na dor nober ducce, na diir cuka mwenger na diir kume tak, tok ti ki “halliluya!” Teluwe maliyar ti, kwama be nii bi kwane gwamme.  
\v 7 Bi ma bititen, bi ne co dur, tak ri bi ne co duktangka wori cika naka be kwame ko nin buu ri nawiye bineu ywelum bwiceu.  
\v 8 Ciin dub co naci dum bwiceu ki kwilendo ki filang kange wo lalang merek koceu yora dutti maniyeu (wori lalang mereko kendo twiya twiyau ki nung cak-cake nangen nob kwama ko wucakke).  
\v 9 Nii tomange wucakke yiye ki “Mulangum wi nob bi bwiyere be buro fiya bicuuwor naci ya fiye cika naka be kwamake.” Cin yiye tak ki, “Mulangum wuro” buro bilenke ti kwama ko.  
\v 10 man yari man canga ken kange mo, kange keb mwebburo tam warke dor Yeesu. ko wab kwama, wori warke dor Yeesu re be warke yuwa tangbe ker dukumer”.  
\v 11 Di la mato dii kwama wumom la ma tok ri mato tuwa fuworko. Cii ki cuwo nii wo yim dor cereu ki nii ci ciya cike kange bilenke. Cike ma warke mor cak-cake ci ma kwenti.  
\v 12 Nuwe ceu kino na biyen kirer la con wiki lalang duwek ducce dorcer. cin wiki den mulangum cinen wo no kebo cori kange nii man wo nyome.  
\v 13 Ci dum ki belle wo cii dokken mor bwiyale. La den cero ki cuwo ti kii ker kwamak.  
\v 14 Nob kwenebo dii kwamau bwang cinen tenti dor tuwa fuwor tini, cii dum ki kwilen lalang merek ko twiya twiyau wo fuwoce ri manki duti takeu.  
\v 15 Mor nyire ce kulendo nyiyo cacau ceuti wo cii torang nubo kumtacilleti cikeu ri can ma liyar cer ki dang kiyemerek. ci fuwarang fiya cokka mweb Inabi ti ki dotange funer kwama nii bikwane gwamme.  
\v 16 Cin wiki den mulangum bellece nen kange ki co “Liya Liyabbe, teluwe, teluwe tini”.  
\v 17 Man to bwe tomange wuccake tim kakuk. Ci cuwo bi cuwor tikidiro dur fiye bilibetini cuto dor re “ko bou, ko mweri wari caka cika ko dur kwama ce.  
\v 18 Ko bou ko no wo nang liyatini nang nubo ne bi weret tiye, nang nubo dure, nang tuwa tini kange nubo kwob ci tiye kange nang nubo gwam, wo ki cerka kange cangabbo nubo kwanneu kange buro man kibi kwanneu.  
\v 19 Man to durtini liyatinimbo dor bitineu kange nob kweneb cebo. Ciki mweri naci te kwen kange wo dor tuware kange nob kweneb ceko.  
\v 20 Cin tam liya dor bitinere durko kange nob tomangeb dukumer cwerke wo merang diker nyimanka ti kaceu. Ki diker nyimangka tini buro cin bolang buro yom yirom biciro wo kange buro ma tati bak-bakeu  
\v 21 Ciin twallangum tangnim cem bo ki kulen do ceru nyi nii wo dor tuwereu. Bilibeu gwam-gwam carangum bilentini ceu.   
\c 20
\p
\v 1 La min to ni nagen kwama yirauti firen di kwama, wiki diker kang cek.  
\v 2 La ci too no cwe charko wuro cho bwekelkele bwamco coro kwini bikate.  
\v 3 Ciin merken co mor buwakke wo manki dikau nung. co kwati dur liyar cerwi dor cer. Nyo na wo kariyilo ci bolangten nubo nyombo ker kwamaere wo adimti coro lam bikate. bwiko wo di tam nyo a nyamkang cimen bi duwar.  
\v 4 La wi man too fitiyimken nubo wuro yim dor cereu chi nubo chi neci bi kwan bolange. Lami to dume nubowo chi mwatang doreu ki ker Yeesu kang ker kwamar. Ci wabo bicirin kange diro cerkangce, chin ko ywoaka cerkangka tikob ci kang kangcik cin fulongum yim cimbo, cin ca liyar kange bibwekwama coro lam bikate.  
\v 5 Tang ni nubo bwiyameu, yilaubo ki dume, no coro bikate dimeri na yimde. Wuro co kwenka nubo bwiyameu ki kaba.  
\v 6 Nii wo fiya calangka wucakeu, co nii wo ki tureni mor kwenka nubo ki kaba. buro wo yobe mani ki bikwan dor nubo wuro. Ciya yilam nubo wab kwama kange bibwe kwama ciya yi liyar kange co ki coro bi kate.  
\v 7 Lano coro bikate lamdi, ciya cikom bwekelkele furcuna.  
\v 8 Can cerken kale na co bolang nubo ti wo nyumbo ker kwamareu, kung nari kalewe Gog kange magog mweranci na kwenece kilatum cembo dong dong kange biyabombo caji yeu.  
\v 9 Cin yati kale wuro ni cin kangtangum fiye nubo ne bilenke wiyeu ci yimwe. La kirako yirau di kwama twirang ci.  
\v 10 Bwekelkele wo bolcitiyeu merken co mor kire wo furko cabie, fiye ci merum nange nicwerke ni wabka ciya nuwa dotange kume kange kakuk bak-ni-bak.  
\v 11 Lami to dikero dor ko kange nubo yim dorcere. kalewo kange di kwama cin cwam tikobcem, la cin manki fiye ciya yakentiye.  
\v 12 Min to nubo kwarangum me nubo dur kange bibei ci tirangum wi kabum na gwomfe la cin wo bifimtini. la ci wom bifimer dumero. Bilendo an macimen bolang ki diker mulangum mor takarau, ki dikero ci maneu.  
\v 13 Wima nubo wanang mureceu. Bwararo kange lo bibwetinim, nubo bwangten mbwanang mureceu ci macimen bolang dong dong kange diker ci maneu.  
\v 14 La ci merken wuro kang lobibwiti kira. Wuro co bwaro wo yobbe bitike Kira.  
\v 15 Kwarub niwo ci fibo dencer mulang mulange mor bifumer dumeri, can merken co kira.   
\c 21
\p
\v 1 La min to dii kwam fwir kange dorbitinero fwir, wori dii kwama wo ki ƙabau kange dorbitiner ƙabako cum, kange wima mani.  
\v 2 Min to cinan loro wucakeu, Urusalima fwirko, wo yirau dii kwama Kwama nin, ywelum ywele na bine ci manten bwayilen ker nina bare cereu.  
\v 3 Min diro dur dor kutile liyare tok ti ki, “To! fiye yime Kwamau kino wari kange nubo fir tini, tak keu ca yi kange cii. Cii an yilam nubo loce, la Kwama ki bwico an yi kange cii, can yilam Kwama ciye.  
\v 4 Can wam mwem nuwem ciyembo wiyak nuwe ciye, bwaro mani a kumti tak, kakaa fir neret, kakaa wiye, kakaa dotange. Dikerro car ko cum.  
\v 5 Co nii wo ci yim dor kutile liyareu yiki,” To! mi yilam ki dikero kwarub fwice.” Con tiki, “Mulangum wuro wori ketito buro daten ciyaka kange bilenke.”  
\v 6 Cin yiye ciki, “Dike buro dim! Min alpha kange omega, terka kange dika ki niwo nuwa dilo mwe tiyeu man nee co noka ki lime nek fiye mwem dumem bo ceruw tiyeu.  
\v 7 Nii wo fiya tureniye ri atin ye kwali dikero buro, la man yilam Kwama ce, co can yilam bibwe mi.  
\v 8 Dila nubo buro tārangi nyeu, nob bwini bilenkeb, nnubo ma dikero ti yei nyeu, nubo twal dortiyeu, nubo ma bwiratum tiyeu, nub buwabbebo, nubo wab fulen tiyeu, kange nob cwerke bo gwam, fiye yime ceu an yila mor kirako diriye. Cuwo bwaro yobeu.  
\v 9 Wiin mor bibei tomange diikwama nibereu bou mi nen, wo ki kwellini niber dim ki fencangê bwiko nibereu, yiki, “Bou fo. man nang mwen bineu fwirko, Bibwe Kwama  
\v 10 La cin tuye mor yuwa tangba cu ki mo bangko durko cwemi nye ri cin dang mencinan loro wucakke Urchalima ceru dii Kwama yirauti fiye Kwama nine.  
\v 11 Uruchalima wiki duktongka Kwamak, wo mim langka ceko kino na bicuka bwayilenne, na terro tiblangti tiblange- wo ki filang na ter dacenner.  
\v 12 Cin wi ki tiyakko duwi duwe, ki nyilotini kwob cilom bo yob, ki nob tomangebo dii kwamau kwob cilombo yob nyilotini ko nin. Dor nyilo tini cin mulangti tuwe loni kwob cilombo yob wo bibei Icraila ciyeu.  
\v 13 Cungako twareu nyiloko wi ta'ar, bangkonin nyiloko ta'ar kwacalmen nyiloko wi ta'ar.  
\v 14 Tiyak cinan loro wiki kwar mukaro kwob cilombo yob, wi dor ciyer takeu dentini nob tomangeb wo Be Kwame Kwama ko kwob cilom bo yobbe.  
\v 15 Co nii wo tokker kange meu, wiki dang mwin nek naci cuwam cinanloro, nyilo ceko kange tiyak ceko.  
\v 16 Cinanloro ci muweu, cuwemtum cembo kino donki donki kange, kwiyatum cembo. Cin cuwam cinanloro ki dank cuwakam, bikateu kwob cilombo yob ki cwemer (Cunga ceko, kwiyatum cembo, kange cwemtum cembo dongi dongi)  
\v 17 Cin cuwam ten tiyak ceko tak, tu tum cembo nako 475.2 ki cuwaka nifirek.( Wo co cuwaka bibei tomange Kwama ko dii kwamau).  
\v 18 Tiyakko cii muki jaspa, la cinanloro ka den mwiner, wo twelum na nuwe turome.  
\v 19 Kwar tiyak kero cin man ten bwayilen ki tero ken. Wo ki kabau jaspa, yobe ceu saffir, taare ceu agat, naare ceu emaral  
\v 20 nunge ceu onis, nukkune ceucardiyus, nibere ceu kimsolat, wo naurube ceu beril, wo teere ceu tofaz, kwobbe ceukirisofaras, wo kwob cilombo wiinee ceu yakinta, kwobcilombo yobe ceu ametis.  
\v 21 Nyiloko kwob cilombo yob beu co kwilen bwayilenero kwob cilombo yobeu; nyilo ki wiin wiine ci ywelang ki kwilen bwayilenero wiin wiin. nur le tini mor cinan loro nineu ci ywilang ki den mwinner na nuwee turome yanglangeu.  
\v 22 Mi tobo bikur waber wi mor cinar loro nin, wori Teeluwe nii bikwane gwam kange Bekwameu cii bikur waber cero.  
\v 23 Cinan loro dobo kakuk kakaa cwiyako na ne filang cinen wori duktangka Kwama ko ne filang koti cinen, la tal kira ceu co Bekwameu.  
\v 24 Nubo kumtaciliu atin ya-yam mor filang cinanlore ko co. Liyatini dor bitinereu atin borangu ki yora ciyeko more ce.  
\v 25 Nyilo tini ceu mani a nung ti ki kakuk, takkeu, kume mani wi.  
\v 26 Ci an bouki yorak kange neka durek nubo kumta ciliu more ce.  
\v 27 La dike kange man wo ki duti yeu a doti more ce. Gwam nii wo ma dike kange ti wo kwenduwe ceu kakaa ki cwerke a dotiye, dila ka nubo buro den ciyero mulangum mor diker mulangkar dumek Bekwame ke.   
\c 22
\p
\v 1 la bibwe tomange wucake, nang men caji mwem dumem wo manki dutiye. ceruti kutile liyar kwama ka-nge be kwameceu  
\v 2 tiber dor nurero cinar lore. bwatiye dume wi kongeni caji nin, wo ne bituti ti wangko kwob culombo yob mor cwiyake. lallu tiye ceu na twaka nobbeko bitentine.  
\v 3 ciilka mani tak. kutile liyar kwama ka-nge be kwame ceu, a nowi cinnar loro nin, cangab cebo an ma nangen cangabero.  
\v 4 ci an to'o tikob cebo, den cero an no'o tikob cib.  
\v 5 kume ka-nge man tak, mani ciya do'o filang tal kiristi kaka filang kakuker, wori Teluwe kwama an wen cinen. ci an ca liyar bak-ni-bak.  
\v 6 bwe tomange wucake yii ye, “kero buro ciyam-ciyam cuko, bilengke tak. Teluwe, kwama yuwa tangbe nob dukume, tom nii tomange ce wucake na nung cangab cebo nin dige a bwiti kutangbe.”  
\v 7 “To'o, mi bouti kutangbo, nii bibwiyere wo tam ker dukumer bifumero weu.”  
\v 8 mo yuwana, mo ma nuwa, to'o digero weu. fiya cuwo ma nuwa ma to'o ciyau, min yarken kabum nani bibwe tomange wucake wo nangkan men citiyeu.  
\v 9 la con yii mare nyo, min nii bwanka na mo, ka-nge yitub mweb nob dukumeb ka-nge buro ne bilengke kero wuro mor bifure wo. “wab kwama;”  
\v 10 yii ye, cumom de ketito, wori kini dadom  
\v 11 wuri manki cakcaka a ca kaba manki cakcake, nii wo ki dutiye, a ca kaba ki fitongka bwiyek cek. nii wo ki cakcake a ca kaba ki cakcake ce. nii wo wucake a kaba ki wucake ce”  
\v 12 “To'o mi bouti kutangbo, ya'aka miko wi kang mik, man ya'a nobo gwam dong-dong ka-nge nangendo ci maneu.  
\v 13 Mo Alpha ka-nge Omega, kaba ka-nge cwile, terka dige ka-nge cwile ce.  
\v 14 Nob bibwiyer nobbo nirum belle ciye na fiya ciyaka na ci ca bwatiye dume, takeu na ci doken cinnar lor nyiilo cek.  
\v 15 kaleu, bicwetini, nob buwab, nob fuleneb, nob kayatum, nob twalkab, ka-nge nobo gwam wo bilang maka digero bwir tiye.  
\v 16 mo Yeesu, min tomu bwe tomange wucake na ne kom warke dige buro na nob bwangka kwama. mo dimer na niya Dauda bitiner burit wo flange.  
\v 17 yuwa tangbe ka-nge bine cin tokki, “bou” wuro nuwari a toki ak-nge ki, “bou” nii wo nuwa dulomwe tiye ka-nge nii wo cwitiye ca bou na ci fiya mwem dumem luma.  
\v 18 mi yii nobbo gwam wo nuwa keti dukume bifumere: no ka-nge yokten dor cer di, kwama an yok cinenten finjange mor bifumero weu.  
\v 19 No ka-nge kwom wi mor ketito wo bifumer dukumereri, kwama an kwob cinen mor tii dume, mor cinar lor wucake, wuro ci mulangi mor bifumere weu.  
\v 20 Nii wuro warker dor dige bure, yii ki, “ong; mi bouti kutangbo” Ati nyo; bou, Teluwe Yeesu;  
\v 21 luma Teluwe be Yeesu a yii ka-nge kom gwam. Ati nyo.   